4Geeks Academy offers a comprehensive course to become an AI Machine Learning Engineer, designed for beginners with no prior knowledge. This 16-week program involves three classes per week, with a maximum of 12 students per class. Students will learn key skills in Python, SQL, Looker, Streamlit, and statistics, and will create predictive models using libraries such as Pandas and Numpy. The curriculum covers both supervised and unsupervised learning, alongside real-life problem-solving. Recognized certificates will be awarded upon completion. Classes are available in English and Spanish. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop